          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 30.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The main sources of uncertainty in the",
                "relative angular distributions are the estimates",
                "of the 160(3He, n0) intensities between 80. and",
                "110. degr. and of backgrounds and the uncertainties in",
                "the relative efficiency of the detector. The latter is",
                "greatest at backward angles and at the lowest",
                "bombarding energies. Here the overall uncertainty",
                "is estimated to be a maximum of 30 % under the most",
                "unfavourable conditions. At higher energies and forward",
                "angles, the uncertainties are mainly due to counting",
                "statistics and very much smaller."
              ]
            }
          ],
